.DT
learn
Discworld player help
learn

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
learn - Learn skills from someone.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
learn <skill> from <person>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This enables you to learn a skill that a person has offered to teach 
you.  You can also teach yourself a skill but this is much more
expensive than getting someone else to teach you.  To teach yourself
a skill you learn a skill from yourself.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> learn fighting from pinkfish
You learn 2 levels of fighting from Pinkfish for 5000 xp.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
skills, teach.
.EP
